name: Kate Plus Date
overview: After nearly a decade of being single, Kate Gosselin teams up with relationship and dating experts to find the perfect match for her.

episodes.name: Somebody to Love
episodes.overview: After more than a decade of being single, Kate Gosselin is finally ready to begin dating; getting help from a matchmaker and twins Mady and Cara, Kate is set up on two very different dates.

episodes.name: Crazy Little Thing Called Love
episodes.overview: With 2 dates under her belt, Kate is ready to see who Rachel has lined up for this week. Jeremiah is a gentle giant and Rosario is an incredible opera singer, but will either one win her over and be in the running for a 2nd date?

episodes.name: Another One Bites the Dust
episodes.overview: Kate feels like she may have had the best and worst dates of her life in the same week; bowling, squash and one not-so-romantic dinner will drive Kate to make some drastic decisions.

episodes.name: I Want To Break Free
episodes.overview: Mady and Cara watch some of Kate's early dates and assess who they think should make it to the second round, while Kate's new matchmaker has a slow start when his first match fails to show up.

episodes.name: Under Pressure
episodes.overview: It's Mady and Cara's turn to interview some of Kate's dates; Kate hits the town with a super jock and a private investigator.
